Body: Description: [Error getting INI file path from registry for host] and [PrepareTask for DC 'SHAREPOINTACCESS' for task 'System Scan' failed: Unspecified error]

What We've Learned Updated: In SPAC log we see:
[C:53] No log location set in configuration for host and no default log location specified, will get log locations from registry
Next Steps Updated: Make sure the SPAC job is properly configured to find the activity logs for SPO
